"controlsBody" = "You play Go Thirteen by dragging across the screen to create groups. Once you've connected a group the numbers of those squares are added to form a new square. All squares that reach the number thirteen dissapear to make room for a new (lower) square. It is not possible to combine squares that would result in a new square that has a number high than 13.";
"goalTitle" = "Goal";
"goalBody" = "The objective of Go Thirteen is to get as high a score as possible. The game is over when there are no more possible moves (because every move would result in a square with a number higher than 13). High numbers are harder to get rid of than lower numbers so make sure that you get rid of them first!";
